text: Secret Agent's Destiny () is a 1970 Soviet adventure movie directed by Venyamin Dorman.«Ты удираешь, а я догоняю». 5 известных ролей Георгия ЖжёноваСУДЬБА РЕЗИДЕНТА (1970) It stars Georgy Zhzhyonov, Mikhail Nozhkin, and Andrei Vertogradov. == Actors == * Georgy Zhzhyonov as Mikhail Tulyev * Mikhail Nozhkin as Pavel Sinitsyn * Andrei Vertogradov as Vladimir Borkov * Yefim Kopelyan as General Sergeev * Rostislav Plyatt as Kazin * Nikolai Prokopovich as Colonel Markov == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1970 movies Category:Soviet adventure movies
title: Secret Agent's Destiny
